entry.title: In Ukraine Talks, Who Is Playing for Time?
entry.content: With talks between the U.S. and Russia over Ukraine continuing into next week, a look under the lid to see who gains more leverage as the diplomatic clock ticks.

entry.title: On Scotland's Haunting Coast, a Village Dreams of Space
entry.content: A new generation of microsatellites is allowing some unlikely players to follow Elon Musk and Jeff Bezos into the space business, but opponents worry about the ecological toll.
